&{template:default} {{name= **Ballista**}} {{Rules =
A ballista is essentially a Huge heavy crossbow fixed in place. 
Its size makes it hard for most creatures to aim it. 
Thus, a Medium creature takes a –4 penalty on attack rolls when using a ballista, 
and a Small creature takes a –6 penalty. 
It takes a creature smaller than Large two full-round actions to reload the ballista after firing.
A ballista takes up a space 5 feet across.
}}